 ³ Grab your oxygen mask and jump into the future of interplanetary          ³

 ³ defense. The year is 2219AD, and Earth’s Star Federation has unleashed    ³

 ³ the R-GRAY advanced tactical combat fighter to save the planet from       ³

 ³ certain destruction at the hands of the bloodthirsty Secilia Federation.  ³

