 ³ will settle for nothing less than complete annhilation of Earth.          ³

 ³ Fortunately, Star command has created two R-GRAY prototypes, so if you    ³

 ³ need extra firepower, a skilled friend can fly at your side. Whether you  ³

 ³ fly solo or with a friend, the intense sound, action, and arcade-perfect  ³

 ³ Hyper-3D visuals will blow you away!    


